Questions YOU Should Ask Interviewer

Very important for senior roles.

Ask:

“How mature is your Kubernetes platform?”
“How are CI/CD and release processes currently managed?”
“What are the biggest operational challenges today?”
“How is observability implemented?”
“Are teams following GitOps or traditional deployments?”
“How are cloud cost optimization initiatives handled?”
“What is the current DevOps team structure?”
“How much ownership does this role have in architectural decisions?”
